{"tid":1382314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國死無賴！！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:42:11.000Z","uid":181165,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"540db346942309055152187496c98e83513617fd","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"好多人唔知點解香港咁重要 <br />\n可以做低整個中國<br />\n同大家係<span style=\"color: gold;\">經濟嘅角度</span>分享下<br />\n<br />\n中國係共產型社會 唔會有自由嘅投資市場<br />\n雖然有股票嘅機制 但一旦跌價10%以上 就會停版<br />\n股票市場冇自由可言 股價一跌 外資又冇得及時撤資會損失慘重<br />\n所以好少外資會係大陸投資<br />\n<br />\n相反香港就有自由市場 而且英國投資左咁多年嘅hardware基建同software金融服務 會吸引到好多外資投資 因為安全<br />\n<br />\n其實依家共產黨 根本就係行緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無賴</span></span>制度<br />\n又要行共產 但又想食自由市場嘅甜頭-資金<br />\n<br />\n而每年係外國經香港流入中國嘅外資大約3000萬億<br />\n係中國gdp 3倍<br />\n就算中國有幾高gdp都好 冇資金 佢乜春都做唔到<br />\n好似間公司咁 你冇資金 請到幾多員工 幾多店鋪 都負擔唔起 一定執好多中少企 <br />\n到時中國經濟 會有大幅度下降趨勢<br />\n類似金融風暴<br />\n<br />\n所以點解香港對中國咁重要 <br />\n因為我地係佢嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">atm</span></span> 用我地嚟禁錢比佢做生意<br />\n但佢<span style=\"color: red;\">恩將仇報</span> 講到我地冇左佢唔得咁 <br />\n自由行同旅遊業佔我地gdp好少咋！你好撚重要？<br />\n離撚晒譜！<br />\n其實係佢冇左我地唔得<br />\n又要靠我地 又要踩低我地<br />\n中國<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死無賴</span></span> ！！！"},{"pid":"f63da7d95356e1005520cdbab51bb52c44b1ef2b","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"推撚爆中國"},{"pid":"2b736ed040ea5aa6fd83d4242bc94fd807bcd7ad","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"無恥之國"},{"pid":"1566dd89c3223c1e41c55e6a71f2d34192d42b57","tid":1382314,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"03a56dc38151d9716c6c5bcb7deee8f1a392dc6a","tid":1382314,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以be water一次<br />\n只守唔攻<br />\n<br />\n再全力狙擊黑警濫暴</span></span>"},{"pid":"2612440e0af6cb754fc01ba97f8c559bf74b617a","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"},{"pid":"451c6fb30c9ea1839fd0b3b19837174d1e3abe6b","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"},{"pid":"2050e7392501f1618341c6309e2980701f6c786f","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1566dd89c3223c1e41c55e6a71f2d34192d42b57","tid":1382314,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"},{"pid":"9fa1359942c060e0887328acf18e85aa20bfeed4","tid":1382314,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a6d55a525bd345269a96aedfccdcb1f96bc74b05","tid":1382314,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,